title.narrative: Stabilisation Advisers for Sudan Recovery Fund

description.narrative: This activity (Stabilisation Advisers for Sudan Recovery Fund) is a component of South Sudan Recovery Fund (SSRF) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £683,210. This component benefits South Sudan, and works in the following sector(s): Social Protection, Road transport, Agricultural development. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 22-07-2011 and the end date is 30-10-2014.
